stock-agent.skill
=================
This file represents the installable skill package.

To create the actual .skill file:
1. Zip the entire stock-agent/ folder
2. Rename the .zip to stock-agent.skill
3. Install via Claude.ai → Settings → Skills → Install Skill

Contents packaged:
- SKILL.md (core skill instructions)
- references/technical-indicators.md
- references/ml-strategy-patterns.md
